Tuning Clustering and Optimization¶

In [40]:
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans

wcss = []

cluster = range(1,15)
In [41]:
for k in range(1,15):
    kmeans2 = KMeans(n_clusters=k)
    kmeans2.fit(df[["Gender","Age","Income","Score"]])
    wcss.append(kmeans2.inertia_)
